.Dd June 9, 2002
.Dt SCHIZO 4 sparc64
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm schizo
.Nd SPARC64 Host/PCI bridge
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "schizo* at mainbus0"
.Cd "pci* at schizo?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
device provides support for the
.Xr pci 4
bus on sparc64
systems, most often found on UltraSPARC III based systems.
It supports the
.Xr ioctl 2
interface in
.Xr pci 4 .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr pci 4 ,
.Xr psycho 4
.Sh HISTORY
.Ox
support for the
.Nm
first appeared in
.Ox 3.2 .
